{"tid":850094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★支人動物園內塞膠袋入河馬口中，放聲大笑！","createTime":"2018-10-06T08:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T15:51:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"746834c6a35aba9ea5275e8183f90a9910a7360e","tid":850094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T08:01:15.000Z","msg":"網傳短片所見，該名身穿白衣的男子帶同小孩翻越河馬池的圍欄，先將一堆爆谷灑向池中的河馬，河馬張口要吃後，男子竟將連帶塑膠袋的爆谷紙盒直接掟入河馬的嘴裏。不知就裏的河馬合口吞食後，男子與旁邊觀眾興奮地笑，竟無人認為有問題及加以制止。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20181006/photo/1006-00178-015b1.jpg?t=1538812828756\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20181006%2Fphoto%2F1006-00178-015b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1538812828756&d=tmnNc1%2F5Cp15QOcWwSiJj8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=9e7d4477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20181006/photo/1006-00178-015b1.jpg?t=1538812828756</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n至於吞食膠袋的河馬，經過獸醫及飼養員檢查之後，目前並無大礙，惟園方稱吞下的膠袋難以由外界取出，只能由河馬自行排出，園方將對其持續觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20181006/photo/1006-00178-015b2.jpg?t=1538812843555\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20181006%2Fphoto%2F1006-00178-015b2.jpg%3Ft%3D1538812843555&h=319ce935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20181006/00178_015.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20181006%2F00178_015.html&d=tmnNc1%2F5Cp15QOcWwSiJj8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=396a12a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20181006/00178_015.html</a>"},{"pid":"e27e52c05d1ddd771c898b714dfe74fc2609ec0a","tid":850094,"uid":26429,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T08:06:07.000Z","msg":"中國人一有咩撚野黃金週假期<br />\n就等於係全球性災難"},{"pid":"e614f6bc129560c9fab7524a953